        <figcaption>穿防化服的军人在导弹发射前做最后的检查工作。（视频截图）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder full"><img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/articles/2023/04/13/0413009.jpg?VersionId=HVUtV1PEOv3CHbKKm6lXIhG0Yrp5lis2" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
